{"tid":2261666,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"涉今年2月及5月網上發表威嚇及煽惑襲警　2男被落案檢控下月4日提堂","createTime":"2020-10-28T13:24:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-29T02:46:48.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"0e3c98fd48275d50552a713c51c988d3e1302cce","tid":2261666,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T13:24:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_info/4194\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_info%2F4194&d=wqADD7%2BrbugmZDmBsEVo7L9EqtgOipuK5hw8%2B6jdv%2Bo%3D&h=827f4db8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_info/4194</a><br />\n<br />\n涉網上發表威嚇及煽惑襲警 2男被落案檢控下月提堂<br />\n<br />\n【東方日報】警方網絡安全及科技罪案調查科留意到有人於本年1月至2月期間，在網上社交媒體針對警務人員發表具威嚇性言論，及煽動他人襲擊警務人員，遂展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n警方經深入調查後，於2月18日上午在觀塘區拘捕一名21歲姓楊本地男子，涉嫌「刑事恐嚇」，及於5月26日上午在灣仔區拘捕一名60歲姓蔡本地男子，涉嫌「煽惑他人有意圖而導致他人身體受嚴重傷害」。<br />\n<br />\n警方經諮詢法律意見後，今日（28日）分別以一項「刑事恐嚇」罪控告該名姓楊被捕男子，另一名姓蔡被捕男子被控以一項「煽惑他人有意圖而導致他人身體受嚴重傷害」罪，案件將於下月4日上午在東區裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n#20201028新聞"},{"pid":"736a5696234d77f1e39c9b731ac654f562da41fc","tid":2261666,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T13:25:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b3114b04437fdcdea6d0044cd8416a46cd1723e","tid":2261666,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T13:25:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>60歲姓蔡本地男子</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"364afdfb3b22966fe7ed0dee044775490b5a666b","tid":2261666,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"cit